#10 Soalan Python (Sequence) - Penyelesaian Masalah Untuk Pemula

#Soalan 1 (Input dan Output asas)
#Create a python program that receives one number from the user and displays the number back to the screen.
#input from user
>>> user_input = input('Enter a number..')
Enter a number..
>>> print('Enter a number: 7',user_input)
Enter a number: 7 
#output from user
>>> print('User entered: 7',user_input)
User entered: 7 

#Soalan 4 (Penggunaan pembolehubah berguna)
#Create a python program that receives the length and width of the rectangle from the user and calculates the area of the rectangle.
>>> #the rectangle length      
>>> length = (input("enter the length of the rectangle:.."))      
enter the length of the rectangle:..
>>> #the rectangle width       
>>> width = (input("enter the width of the rectangle:.."))    
enter the width of the rectangle:..
>>> #calculates the area of the rectangle
>>> input_area = ("length*width")       
>>> print(input_area)   
length*width
>>> print("the area of the rectangle is:..", input_area)      
the area of the rectangle is:.. length*width

